
                      The Blue Wave Offline Mail Reader
                                 Version 2.30
                            Official Beta Testers

   The following compilation of names includes all of the people who helped to
   make version 2.30 what it is today.   Several megabytes of test copies have
   travelled considerable distances for the sole purpose of making sure you
   have a working, as-close-to-bug-free-as-possible release.  I guarantee you
   that without these people, the reader wouldn't be half of what it is today.

   Why not take a few moments to send a message to one of these people,
   thanking them for their unselfishness and hard work?  Not only is there
   work involved, but considerable cost involved with polling Flint, Michigan,
   USA twice per week!

   Here they are, listed in no special order (other than alphabetical):

